* [[Françoise Bottéro]]: Revisiting the wen and the zi: The Great Chinese Characters Hoax. Bulletin of the Museum of Far Eastern Antiquities 74, 2002, p. 14-33 [[@http://crlao.ehess.fr/docannexe.php?id=646|pdf]]
* [[Françoise Bottéro]]: Chinese Characters Versus Other Writing Systems: The Song Origins of the Distinction Between "Non-Compound Characters" and "Compound Character". In Meaning and Form, eds. Ken-ichi Takashima and Jiang Shaoyu. Lincom, 2004

